<p class="p0 c18"><span>11</span><span class="c16"> 见范应元《老子道德经古本集注》，《中华道藏》本。</span><span class="c16"></span></p>
<p class="p0 c18"><span class="c16"></span></p>
<p class="p0 c19"><span class="c16">（作者系香港青松观主席）</span><span class="c16"></span></p>
